    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>chickpeas</strong></p><p>Dissolve <strong>half</strong> your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
