    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, add your <strong>drained chickpeas</strong>, <strong>halved green beans </strong>and <strong>diced apricots</strong> to the pan</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for a 12-15 min or until the green beans are tender – this is your <strong>Moroccan-style chickpeas</strong></p>",
