      "instruction": "<p>Place your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> on a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until the almonds are lightly browned, then remove from the oven and leave to cool</p><p>Tip: Watch these like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
