      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Moroccan-style chickpeas</strong> with the <strong>lemony</strong> <strong>couscous</strong> to the side and sprinkle the <strong>toasted almonds </strong>over the top</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
